headline: UBS Raises Kroger Price Target After Strong Q1 Earnings
summary: The Kroger Co. (NYSE:KR) ranks among the best FMCG stocks to buy. On June 23, UBS maintained its Neutral rating on The Kroger Co. (NYSE:KR) and raised its price target for the grocery store chain’s stock from $66 to $74 on June 23. The price target raise comes after Kroger’s first-quarter earnings, which UBS reported […]
